      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## Saving a Cats v Dogs Model"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "98d53c05"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "This is a minimal example showing how to train a fastai model on Kaggle/Colab, and save it so you can use it in your app."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "7Es-UbxPtrPH"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Make sure we've got the latest version of fastai:\n",
        "!pip install -Uqq fastai"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "evvA0fqvSblq",
        "_kg_hide-input": true,
        "_kg_hide-output": true,
        "execution": {
          "iopub.status.busy": "2022-05-03T05:51:37.948558Z",
